nd the middle east the company operates in two segments capital markets and asset management within the capital markets segment the… morejefferies group along with its subsidiaries operates as an investment bank and institutional securities company throughout the americas europe asia and the middle east the company operates in two segments capital markets and asset management within the capital markets segment the companys operations consist of sales trading and research in equity derivatives initial public offerings hedge funds pension and profit sharing programs and investmentgrade fixed income securities within the asset management segment the company offers investment management services and products to various private investment firms jefferies group along with its subsidiaries operates as an investment bank and institutional securities company throughout the americas europe asia and the middle east the company operates in two segments capital markets and asset management within the capital markets segment the… morejefferies group along with its subsidiaries operates as an investment bank and institutional securities company throughout the americas europe asia and the middle east the company operates in two segments capital markets and asset management within the capital markets segment the companys operations consist of sales trading and research in equity derivatives initial public offerings hedge funds pension and profit sharing programs and investmentgrade fixed income securities within the asset management segment the company offers investment management services and products to various private investment firms jefferies group operates in various business units within the it including investment banking the it department is divided into three areas of it shared services the companys primary data center is located in new jersey in addition to a colocation disaster recovery data center an additional disaster recovery data center was build out in stamford ct in  within the infrastructure division the telecommunications group is multifaceted and focuses on telecom networking services database management is another subset of the division and deals with managing the full data lifecycle another subset is windows server support the applications division includes equities trading applications and corporate software development the correspondent services group provides application support across key business units for the company the unix systems management group is the final division which has an implementation and system support group that oversees the lifecycle of jefferies unix systems the information security group monitors the companys it change management process and works directly with it audit and sox it compliance technology procurement is an additional specialized unit that plays a role in it but is not located within the it department the company relies on an in house customized relationship management system called jefbase which tracks financial data and customers for jefferies group employees additionally the company houses virtualized unix and windows servers along with a cisco networking environment its databases are oraclebased sector industry financial brokerage and asset management financial financial services employees  revenue b fye  breaking news on investment signals date type inside scoop  staffing topic finance staffing company jefferies group inc new york ny opportunity seeking an expense controller investment banking – ib management new york ny   staffing topic compliance staffing company jefferies group inc new york ny opportunity seeking an operational  data reporting compliance officer new york ny   staffing topic staffing finance company jefferies group inc new york ny opportunity seeking a junior accountant alternative investments jfin new york ny  want full access to this profile and more rainkings clients have access to over  new investment signals published daily which provide insights on spe